extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Recipe Collection], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The collection has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Recipes:] !{data.recipe_count}
      li #[strong Cuisines:] !{data.cuisine_count}
